## 🎯 Project: **KiteDesk** — Pay-Per-Task AI Research Agent

**One-liner:** An autonomous AI agent that executes research/data tasks on demand, charges USDC per task via Kite chain, and stores attestations on-chain as proof of work.

This hits **every judging criterion** cleanly:
- ✅ Agent autonomy — no human involvement after task submit
- ✅ Real-world — pay-per-use AI APIs is a live market
- ✅ Agentic Commerce — agent-to-API payments, USDC settlement
- ✅ Kite attestations — on-chain proof of task completion
- ✅ Live demo on Vercel

---

