## 🏗️ Core User Flow (Keep It Simple)

```
User connects wallet
       ↓
Selects task type + enters prompt
       ↓
Agent quotes price (e.g. 0.10 USDC)
       ↓
User approves USDC tx on Kite chain
       ↓
Agent executes task autonomously
       ↓
Result returned + attestation written on-chain
       ↓
User sees result + tx proof link
```

