## 1. PROJECT OVERVIEW

KiteDesk is a pay-per-task AI agent platform where users submit real-world tasks (research, code review, content generation), pay a small USDC fee via the Kite AI blockchain, and receive autonomous AI execution — with every task cryptographically attested on-chain as proof of work.

**Core Loop:**
```
Connect Wallet → Select Task → Pay USDC via Kite → Agent Executes → Result + On-chain Attestation
```

**Why this wins:**
- Hits every judging criterion (autonomy, commerce, attestation, real-world use)
- Simple enough to ship fully in 2 days
- Live Vercel demo with real wallet + real chain transactions
- Unique: agents that earn and prove their work on-chain

