5. Create lib/constants.ts from Section 6

Rules:
- No emojis in code or comments
- TypeScript strict mode
- No console.logs except in error handlers
- Dark theme from the start (globals.css with CSS variables from Section 15)
- Every file should have a one-line comment at the top: // KiteDesk | [filename purpose]
```

